OL,3,CWelsh rugby braced for radical shake-
OL,4,Cup as proposed cut to two teams
OL,5,Cconfirmed
OL,7,FWelsh rugby bosses propose halving
OL,8,Fprofessional teams to two. ITV News
OL,9,FWales Reporter Rhys Williams has the
OL,10,Flatest
OL,12,F"Let go of the past and imagine the
OL,13,Ffuture."
OL,15,FThat was the message from the Welsh
OL,16,FRugby Union's Director of Rugby, Dave
OL,17,FReddin, to supporters on Wednesday as
OL,18,Fhe set out the most radical shake-up
OL,19,Fof the game in Wales for a generation.
