OL,3,CWelsh rugby braced for radical shake-
OL,4,Cup as proposed cut to two teams
OL,5,Cconfirmed
OL,7,FUnion officials insist funding has
OL,8,Fbeen stretched too thin for too long,
OL,9,Fwith mounting debts and rising player
OL,10,Fcosts pushing the professional game to
OL,11,Fbreaking point.
OL,13,FConcentrating talent into two elite
OL,14,Fsquads, they argue, will help Wales
OL,15,Fretain more of its best players and
OL,16,Fcreate teams capable of competing in
OL,17,FEurope and the United Rugby
OL,18,FChampionship. They also claim it will
OL,19,Fstrengthen the national side, which is
OL,20,Farguably at its lowest ebb in history.
