OL,12,FBut the plan has already provoked
OL,13,Ffierce criticism. Many supporters are
OL,14,Funhappy that the Welsh Rugby Union
OL,15,F(WRU) would assume total control over
OL,16,Fthe rugby operations of both surviving
OL,17,Fclubs. Critics warn the move risks
OL,18,Falienating loyal supporters who follow
OL,19,Fthe four professional sides week in,
OL,20,Fweek out.
